de: Minky Momo travels to an island where she finds a land of children and gets tangled up in an absurd, no-holds-barred standoff against the world's nations. Has "Dr. Strangelove" references.
nm: Magical Princess Minky Momo: La Ronde in my Dream
jp: Mahou no Princess Minky Momo: Yume no Naka no Rondo
